description:
Global probability and parametric isolation grids (netCDF) for &quot;A Global Probabilistic Prediction of Cold Seeps and Associated Seafloor Fluid Expulsion Anomalies (SEAFLEAs)&quot; 

 Probability grid shows the probability of encountering a fluid expulsion anomaly on a global 5 x 5 arc minute grid using the methods in the above manuscript (Figure 2). 

 Parametric isolation shows the most distinct locations globally (Figure S1).

